        "Hmm.....Man, I HATE Autobots!  And of course, I am hating these
Predacons, who think they are like us!  I mean, they SUCK!  Decepticon
sounds sooo much more cooler than Predacon!  We are the Decepticons!  WE
RULE!" He yelled firing his gun in a circle shape.
